221
00:19:01,980 --> 00:19:03,210
[vibrant youth with your presence.]

222
00:19:04,300 --> 00:19:07,100
♪We still have to part from each other♪

223
00:19:07,580 --> 00:19:11,770
♪I'm faint-hearted to stop you from leaving♪

224
00:19:12,870 --> 00:19:15,150
♪Amidst the grieving woods♪

225
00:19:15,530 --> 00:19:18,040
♪Who is crying out there♪

226
00:19:21,270 --> 00:19:24,230
♪I still relentlessly hold on♪

227
00:19:24,760 --> 00:19:29,110
♪I refuse to accept this destiny♪

228
00:19:30,060 --> 00:19:32,440
♪Desperately searching♪

229
00:19:32,730 --> 00:19:34,860
♪Any signs of you♪

230
00:19:38,280 --> 00:19:41,980
♪The bleak Star Forest,
illuminating in the moonlight♪

231
00:19:42,120 --> 00:19:46,650
♪In your eyes, the world never changes♪

232
00:19:47,160 --> 00:19:51,790
♪Yearning grows and interweaves with the past♪

233
00:19:52,030 --> 00:19:58,830
♪Aside from promise,
I have much that I haven't told you♪

234
00:19:59,050 --> 00:20:03,150
♪You are the memory I refuse to let go♪

235
00:20:03,340 --> 00:20:07,370
♪And the craziness of my desperation♪

236
00:20:07,580 --> 00:20:08,780
♪Can you hear♪

237
00:20:09,210 --> 00:20:11,110
♪My calls♪

238
00:20:11,350 --> 00:20:13,240
♪Breaking through extreme dolours♪

239
00:20:13,240 --> 00:20:16,040
♪Rushing towards your embrace♪

240
00:20:16,230 --> 00:20:20,380
♪You are the only one
I dreamt to comb my hair♪

241
00:20:20,380 --> 00:20:24,600
♪And the wish I made upon a star♪

242
00:20:24,780 --> 00:20:26,140
♪One day♪

243
00:20:26,360 --> 00:20:28,810
♪You will turn up gorgeously♪

244
00:20:28,970 --> 00:20:30,940
♪And hold my hands♪

245
00:20:31,150 --> 00:20:37,160
♪To envisage our future♪

246
00:20:40,040 --> 00:20:40,600
[Next episode]

247
00:20:40,600 --> 00:20:41,630
Let's battle for victory!

248
00:20:41,930 --> 00:20:44,460
-Then let's start.
-We need to finish the test faster...

249
00:20:45,000 --> 00:20:45,790
and go back to the Continent sooner

250
00:20:46,230 --> 00:20:47,260
to battle against Martial Soul Empire.

251
00:20:47,730 --> 00:20:49,060
We can't wait for defeat.

252
00:20:49,330 --> 00:20:51,430
A top craftsman trains thoroughly.

253
00:20:51,560 --> 00:20:53,730
Gengxin Town? How could this happen?

254
00:20:54,000 --> 00:20:55,260
You tried your best.

255
00:20:55,300 --> 00:20:59,230
The Ninth Soul Skill attacks your domain
and body comprehensively.

256
00:20:59,560 --> 00:21:01,330
You definitely won't be able to fight back.

257
00:21:01,660 --> 00:21:05,230
The God of the Ocean won't tolerate
any shortcuts.

258
00:21:05,500 --> 00:21:09,190
The upcoming tests will be even harder.
I wish you success.

